  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Park is offered on a half board basis with breakfast and dinner taken in the hotels restaurant.</p>
<p>Breakfast consists of a continental buffet with hot and cold options.</p>
<p>Dinner includes a 4 course evening menu served five evenings a week. The hotel restaurant is closed on Wednesday and Thursday evenings.</p>
<p>There is a weekly fondue and local speciality evening.</p>
<p>A Christmas and New Year gala dinner is included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
