  <description><![CDATA[<p>This charming award-winning family-run hotel enjoys a quiet yet central location and is only a short walk to the Alpin Express lift. The friendly owners Jutta and Patrick Rossi-Bumann look forward to welcoming you.</p>
<h2>Traditional Swiss stay</h2>
<p>The Hotel Park is a great option for those of you wanting to experience a stay in the mountains that is traditionally Swiss. This Hotel is an excellent good-value base with comfortable rooms, good food and a friendly atmosphere and the hotel promotes it's importance of quality, authenticity and closeness to nature. </p>
<h2>Food and drink</h2>
<p><span>During your stay you can expect to enjoy Swiss cuisine with influences from French and Italian dishes. The hotel provides a four course evening meal six nights a week occasionally featuring local specialities from the Valais region. On Thursday evenings you will need to make your own arrangements, but this won't be a problem as the hotel is located in the heart of resort so you'll find a range of restaurants and bars available on your doorstep.</span></p>]]></description>
